1️⃣ Material Creation (MM01)

Maintain QM View

Activate inspection type 01 (GR for PO) or 04 (GR for Production)

Enable: Post to inspection stock

2️⃣ Create MICs (QS21)

Create a Quantitative characteristic
Example: Weight (Range: 9.5–10.5 kg)

Create a Qualitative characteristic
Example: Color (OK / NOT OK)

3️⃣ Create Inspection Plan (QP01)

Assign material & plant

Add operation (ex: 0010 – Quality Check)

Insert MICs

Save the plan

4️⃣ Trigger an Inspection Lot

Create PO (ME21N)

Perform GR (MIGO)

System auto-creates inspection lot

Check via QA32

5️⃣ Record Results (QE51N / QA32 → Results)

Enter measured values

Mark characteristics as accepted/rejected

Save results

6️⃣ Usage Decision (QA11)

Select UD code (e.g., AQL Accepted / Rejected)

System posts stock to Unrestricted / Blocked Stock
